{
    "AWSTemplateFormatVersion": "2010-09-09",
    "Description": "QS(0023) - This template deploys a WSUS server. This template is intended to be installed into an existing VPC that was built using the sample reference architecture titled: \"Implementing Active Directory Domain Services in the AWS Cloud\" **WARNING** This template creates Amazon EC2 Windows instance and related resources. You will be billed for the AWS resources used if you create a stack from this template.",
